precis:
ORDER RESTRICTING CERTAIN IMMUNITY IN RELATION TO THE UNITED STATES which
restricts the immunity extended under this Act to certain USA legal
entities in order to achieve equivalence with the corresponding immunity
extended under the USA Foreign Sovereign Immunities Act to foreign
(including Canadian) legal entities.
